title: Exclusive Quantico Sneak Peek: Uh-Oh! Simon Is On to Ryan
text:
For an undercover agent tailing Alex, Ryan doesn't seem to be doing too good of a job being discreet on Quantico .
On Sunday's episode, Ryan ( Jake McLaughlin ) calls Simon ( Tate Ellington ) creepy, which, while accurate, is also very pot-meet-kettle.
"What is it that makes me creepy?" Simon asks him in the exclusive sneak peek above. "Does it make me creepy that I notice you get up every time Alex [ Priyanka Chopra ] leaves the room? Or that you go on long runs in the woods by yourself? Or that you somehow seem to know this campus like the back of your hand?"
How does Ryan react? Watch the clip to find out.
